Package: plFA
Title: Fast pairwise likelihood estimation of factor models for ordinal
    data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Giuseppe", "Alfonzetti", , "giuseppe.alfonzetti@uniud.it", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6118-6553")),
    person("Haziq", "Jamil", , "haziq.jamil@gmail.com", 
           role = "aut",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3298-1010"))
  )
Description: The plFA package provides a fast implementation of numerical
    and stochastic pairiwse likelihood estimation for latent variable
    models with ordinal data.
